Diamond::

She looked at the print out and wondered who this Darkfate was.  She 
looked up at Devilduer as she got Zardus transmission. "OK, let's get 
her into a cr and lock her inside. She can stay there until we get 
back. Then, I need you to show me your armory. I need a few weapons. 
A long range sniper rifle, a few concusion bombs, two localized EMP 
grenades and a few small photon cannons. Do you think you have them?"

(localized EMP grenades act like a normal EMP except it only effects 
a 10 yard radius area.  If this is not allowed, let me know)
